The summary function provides a summary of a "garma_model" object.

summary.garma_model.Rd

The summary function provides a summary of a "garma_model" object.

# S3 method for garma_model
summary(mdl, verbose = TRUE)

Arguments

mdl

(garma_model) The garma_model from which to print the values.
verbose

(bool) whether to print out the verbose version of the model or not. Default: TRUE

Examples

data(AirPassengers)
ap  <- as.numeric(diff(AirPassengers,12))
mdl <- garma(ap,order=c(9,1,0),k=0,method='CSS',include.mean=F)
summary(mdl)
